# ── Dependencies (restore with `npm install` in Miscellelous) ──
**/node_modules/

# ── Android / Gradle build outputs & caches (regenerated by the build) ──
**/build/
**/.gradle/
**/.cxx/
**/captures/
*.iml
.idea/
# Machine-specific SDK path (Android Studio / `npx cap open` regenerates it)
local.properties

# ── Secrets: keep the signing key and its passwords OUT of source control ──
**/*.keystore
**/keystore.properties
**/signing-key-info.txt

# ── Old build artifacts ──
Grocery - Google Play package/previous-v1.0/

# ── OS / editor cruft ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
